<title>ạ̉rfʿ ʿyny ạ̹ly̱ ạljbạl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉rfʿ
 ʿyny ạ̹ly̱ ạljbạl mn ḥytẖ yạ̉ty ʿwny mʿwnty
 mn ʿnd ạlrb ṣạnʿ ạlsmạwạt wạlạ̉rḍ ạllh
 ḥb mnh ḥyạẗ ạllh ḥb yḥbny dwmaⁿạ ạ̉gẖny yswʿ
 rby qd wfy̱ dyny yswʿ rby kẖlṣny ạllh
 ḥb ṭbyb nfsy ạllh ḥb yḥfẓny hdẖh
 ạlmḥbẗ fạḍt fy qlby hdẖh ạlmḥbẗ tḥyṭny</lyrics>
</song>